     "text": "WARNING : Do not perform the hydraulic circuit control if the hydraulic circuit is not well filled-in.",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1200,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "To check if the hydraulic circuit is well filled-in:",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9885
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "If the pedal is hard, you can perform the hydraulic circuit control",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1320,
      "top": 3360,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 6480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Stop the engine and press 3 times the brake pedal:",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 720,
      "top": 2400,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 7680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "If the pedal is soft : air is present in the primary hydraulic circuit ==> perform the hydraulic bleeding procedure",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1320,
      "top": 2760,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 6960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Hydraulic circuit control :",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 3360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "A - Keep pressed the brake pedal",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 5154
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "C - Start the routine control by pushing the button of the approprate wheel (routine time = 4 sec)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 6000,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 5154
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "B - Another person have to try to manually turn the wheel to test",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 5280,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 5154
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Remark : Routines have to be started one by one (simultaneous controls are forbidden)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 7920,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 6120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "D - During the routine, if the selected wheel is successively blocked/unblocked ==> Control is OK",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
